Description of Samples

UDIO_DATASET_C$IEP <- factor(UDIO_DATASET_C$IEP,
                             levels = c(1, 0),
                             labels = c("IEP", "Non-IEP"))
label(UDIO_DATASET_C$IEP) <- "IEP Status"

UDIO_DATASET_C$ELL <- factor(UDIO_DATASET_C$ELL,
                             levels = c(1, 0),
                             labels = c("ELL", "Non-ELL"))
label(UDIO_DATASET_C$ELL) <- "ELL Status"

UDIO_DATASET_C$FARMS1 <- factor(UDIO_DATASET_C$FARMS,
                             levels = c(1, 0),
                             labels = c("Free/Reduced Lunch", "Non-Free/Reduced Lunch"))
label(UDIO_DATASET_C$FARMS1) <- "Socioeconomic Status"

UDIO_DATASET_C$GRADE <- factor(UDIO_DATASET_C$GRADE,
                             levels = c(6, 7, 8),
                             labels = paste("Grade", as.character(6:8)))
label(UDIO_DATASET_C$GRADE) <- "Grade"

UDIO_DATASET_C$GENDER <- factor(UDIO_DATASET_C$GENDER,
                             labels = c("Female", "Male"))
label(UDIO_DATASET_C$GENDER) <- "Gender"

UDIO_DATASET_C$RACE <- factor(UDIO_DATASET_C$RACE,
                             labels = c("White", 
                                        "Black or African American",
                                        "Hispanic or Latino",
                                        "Asian or Pacific Islander",
                                        "Alaska Native or American Indian",
                                        "Two or more races"))
label(UDIO_DATASET_C$RACE) <- "Race"

mergeDesc(
  getDescriptionStatsBy(factor(rep(1, nrow(UDIO_DATASET_C)),labels = "Total"), UDIO_DATASET_C$GRADE, digits = 1, add_total_col = "last", hrzl_prop = TRUE),

  getDescriptionStatsBy(UDIO_DATASET_C$ELL, UDIO_DATASET_C$GRADE, digits = 1, add_total_col = "last"),

Descriptive Stats of Outcome Variables

sample_size <- function(x) {
  sum(!is.na(x))
}

mean_sd <- function(col) {
  sprintf("%.2f (%.2f)", mean(col, na.rm = TRUE), sd(col, na.rm = TRUE))
}

label(sample_size) <- "n"
label(mean_sd) <- "Mean (SD)"

rapid_descriptive <- tabular( GRADE*FARMS ~ (
  Heading("Reading Comprehension (Pre)")*PRE_RAPID_RC_AB + 
  Heading("Reading Comprehension (Post)")*POST_RAPID_RC_AB + 
  Heading("Writing Composite (Pre)")*PRE_WIAT_COMP + 
  Heading("Writing Composite (POST)")*POST_WIAT_COMP)*((Heading(n)*sample_size)+(Heading("Mean (s.d.)")*mean_sd)), data = UDIO_DATASET_C)
